diagrams.code:
direction right
// AgentNet Decentralized Coordination Flowchart
title AgentNet Decentralized Coordination Flowchart

// Groups and nodes
Setup [color: lightblue, icon: settings] {
  Agent initialization [shape: oval, color: lightblue, icon: user]
  Environment initialization [shape: oval, color: lightblue, icon: server]
}

Execution Phase [color: lightgreen, icon: activity] {
  Local perception [shape: rectangle, color: lightgray, icon: eye]
  Communication step [shape: rectangle, color: lightyellow, icon: message-circle]
  Consensus update [shape: rectangle, color: orange, icon: users]
  Action selection [shape: rectangle, color: lightgray, icon: play]
  Environment interaction [shape: rectangle, color: lightgray, icon: globe]
  Receive reward [shape: parallelogram, color: lightgreen, icon: award]
}

Learning Phase [color: lightblue, icon: book] {
  Collect experience [shape: rectangle, color: lightgray, icon: archive]
  Build local batch [shape: rectangle, color: lightgray, icon: layers]
  Share experience [shape: rectangle, color: lightyellow, icon: upload]
  Update policy [shape: rectangle, color: lightgray, icon: refresh-cw]
}

// Relationships
Agent initialization > Local perception
Environment initialization > Environment interaction
Local perception > Communication step: local state
Communication step > Consensus update: aggregated messages
Consensus update > Action selection: updated parameters
Action selection > Environment interaction: selected action
Environment interaction > Receive reward: reward signal
Collect experience > Build local batch
Build local batch > Share experience: local batch
Share experience > Update policy: aggregated experiences
Execution Phase > Learning Phase: environment feedback
Learning Phase > Execution Phase: policy parameters
